      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a start. the mom stuff is good. can u go deeper with the family gathering thing? like, what are some of the more specific, \"classic\" things that happen at those big cookouts or reunions? maybe some of the more \"intense\" stuff that everyone knows happens, like the loud arguments or how people act when they're trying to prove something. just give me some specific scenarios i can use for a bit.",
